Jacques Dynam https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Dynam 0 Jacques Dynam (30 December 1923 – 12 November 2004) was a French film actor. He appeared in more than 150 films between 1942 and 2004, among which the Fantomas saga. He was born and died in Paris, France.
